{"tid":1916604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（求泛民同佢打手答下我）其實泛民係美港交流會有冇同美國提及香港人要普選？？","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T03:45:02.000Z","uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"668fa8069fe51c83a9ed574201b650ef055400e4","tid":1916604,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:22:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200308/s00002/1583605745313/%E3%80%8A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E4%BF%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%88%B6%E6%AD%A2%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200308%2Fs00002%2F1583605745313%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%258B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=1bfb49e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200308%2Fs00002%2F1583605745313%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%258B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA&h=8e237d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200308/s00002/1583605745313/%E3%80%8A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E4%BF%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%88%B6%E6%AD%A2%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】行政會議召集人陳智思，行會成員張國鈞、葉劉淑儀、廖長江，以及3名泛民立法會議員莫乃光、梁繼昌和譚文豪，應邀到美國出席由美國非政府組織World Affairs Council主持的「美港交流會」，各人於當地時間昨日討論去年通過的《香港人權與民主法案》，美國國務院5月將公布首份香港報告。民主派昨發新聞稿，其中莫乃光要求美方在報告中需加入前瞻要求，如警告港府在未來選舉不能再以「政治審查」取消候選人資格。<br />\n<br />\n張國鈞籲華府懸崖勒馬<br />\n《法案》通過後，美國國務卿將每年審視香港自治情况，決定是否繼續給予特殊地位，以及授權華府可制裁侵害香港人權者。張國鈞在facebook匯報會議情况，稱美國政界通過《法案》是因對香港有很多誤解，並說泛民恐嚇要向美方提出把香港官員和公務員放入制裁名單，令他們工作「縛手縛腳」，會破壞香港高度自治，冀美方懸崖勒馬。<br />\n<br />\n3名泛民議員關注《法案》啟動機制，認為應盡快公布執行細節，讓港人有正式途徑提供證據。梁繼昌引述美國國務院代表再次向港人保證，《法案》中已有條文保障所有受政治檢控的港人，美國駐港領事亦重申絕不會以此為由拒絕批出美國簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------<br />\n早係1月幾既時候，我響應連登巴打呼籲，一人一封電郵寄去泛民，結果得公民黨覆我。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWp4p8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWp4p8Z.png&h=b4a60087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先唔理你哋唔覆同HEA鳩我，但我想問下有唔少人係你哋泛民FB同TWITTER留言要2020普選立法會，例如<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/charlesmok/status/1236640091163918336?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharlesmok%2Fstatus%2F1236640091163918336%3Fs%3D19&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=87921cb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharlesmok%2Fstatus%2F1236640091163918336%3Fs%3D19&h=f3a287dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/charlesmok/status/1236640091163918336?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n民意係點你地好清楚啦。 你地話進攻功能組別我都唔理你，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最低限度你都畀我知道你有冇同美國嗰邊講香港人2020要普選立法會。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b589e43dbfbf9d4ad0bc072d278c811c1c837972","tid":1916604,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5a3s7o8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5a3s7o8.gif&h=9bd65368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5a3s7o8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5a3s7o8.gif&h=9bd65368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5a3s7o8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5a3s7o8.gif&h=9bd65368&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7da7b8b59fe00b3d275862f35408e8e2b99f1d34","tid":1916604,"uid":26846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一國兩制運作良好"},{"pid":"4e19db0714721d39b7f4a0b0afe9dfab5dd6d6d8","tid":1916604,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:27:59.000Z","msg":"你地出一句聲，好過我哋無名小卒講100句話。"},{"pid":"c41b95cf30ff5b7e8cf5899f78e13e08a331c40e","tid":1916604,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTQrDxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTQrDxG.png&h=ef4ebb61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b7f1a79d8ffebbd28e2e41eb2305db6ec5787f4","tid":1916604,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c41b95cf30ff5b7e8cf5899f78e13e08a331c40e","tid":1916604,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTQrDxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTQrDxG.png&h=ef4ebb61&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2123cdf310e10ffe736393b8d932adc7d82f90aa","tid":1916604,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:45:02.000Z","msg":"班大金主要求佢地同美國講一國兩制運作良好既話, 佢地敢唔講咩?"}]}